Dependency Tree

  • edu.umn.biomedicus:biomedicus-measures:jar:2.0.1
    BioMedICUS Measures

    Description: A lightweight (small and dependency-free) Java 8 library for identifying and normalizing numbers and measurements in text. This was developed as a stand-alone component of BioMedICUS, a biomedical and clinical NLP engine developed by the NLP-IE Group at the University of Minnesota Institute for Health Informatics.

    URL: https://github.com/nlpie/biomedicus-measures
